                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>New York</placeName>\n                <date>Aug 26. 51</date>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Sir!</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Allow me to introduce to you <persName>Dr<lb/>\n                    Zim<add>m</add>erman</persName>, a man, well instructed and who would<lb/> like\n                to get a situation as teacher. If you could help<lb/> him to a place, you would\n                oblige me very much; and<lb/> I would be very happy, if he could find a\n                situation<lb/> like that of <persName>Dr. Lehwess<add>?</add></persName>, who after\n                having been some„<lb/>time in <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>, got such a\n                pleasant situation.<lb/> Do for him, what you can, as he is without any<lb/> means\n                whatever and oblige Yours truly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">D. Lilienthal</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3j46m/canvas/p2"
                }
